Imagine what life will look like in 2 or 3 months from now. Did you do your part? Did you stay at home? Did you go to work so we could have food and supplies? Did you walk into that hospital room to save a life? Did you answer the call to help someone who is sick?  To all of our essential workers and first responders who are working hard and saving our lives, thank you all!  We are in this together from all of us to all of you stay home and stay safe!
.

node.text: Ok so i am officially done decorating my daughter’s room !💖 she is starting middle school this upcoming year , and wanted a more big girl theme! So to transition her from little girl to tween I decided to use black as a accent color 🖤 with mixed metal decor pieces ..and rustic touches from her wall decor frames.. lastly  a very chic glamorous wall glitter  art 🖼 piece that i am in-love with! I hope you all enjoy!  #zgalleriemoment#decorforkids#kidsroomideas#pier1love#inspiremehome#farahmehri#decorglamsquad#hobbylobby#hometour#roomtour#rossfinds#amazon#roomdecor

node.text:
Hello friend ! How’s your weekend coming along ? Mine is coming along great! Today I was deep cleaning all downstairs … 

I am getting ready for the next season 😜 washing my all the sheets , curtains , rugs , linens etc & going through my decor and making sure everything has its place in my home or else it’s getting out away .

I woke up early today to check that off my list ! I also threw in a roast  in the oven for dinner 🥘 

Here’s a little vlog I did as I went about my day 
 
Now it’s time to unwind & relax. 

I just love being home 🏡 🥰

Stay tuned on Monday come back to my stories ! I have something I want to share with you! 

With that being said I hope you are having a good weekend 😘

node.text:
Coffee station clean & restock 

Happy Monday! I had a little tidying up I did this morning in my coffee station. I cleaned my @michaelaram canisters with dish soap and warm water & wipes dry . I did the same for my coffee machine . 

I bought new organizers for my cabinets and drawers I’ll be sharing with you sometime this week how I organize the rest of my station! 

I linked up my butterfly 🦋 collection that is currently on sale on my stories ! 

Left the sound on & sharing a clip of my boys in the background 😘 #momlife 

https://ltk.app.link/gH84W2A61hb

node.text:
Cleaning my stove with me🌿
I shared this video a few months ago here & I thought since it’s Sunday cleaning & refill day why not share a little #cleaningmotivation 

Here is a natural way to clean your stove using @dawndishwash @armandhammer baking soda & vinegar . 

Make a paste with the 3 ingredients & scrub! In this video I am using my tool attachment you can find the link  on my highlights 

I also used the same ingredients & soaked the stove grates & burners .. 

Have a wonderful Sunday ! 

#cleaninghacks #cleanwithpassion #cleanhome #cleanhouse #tidy#tidyup #tidyhousetidymind #asmrsounds #naturalcleaning #homehacks #reels#reelinstagram #kitchencleaning #stovetop #amazonfind #amazonfinds

Iced coffee break 🌬
I whipped up a delicious cajeta & #mazapán  iced coffee ☕️ this afternoon I thought I share with you how I made it .. I love being in the kitchen that is where I get creative the most 💫

This was Just the right amount of energy I need to get me going ! We are in the middle of a mini renovation in my youngest daughter Victoria’s bedroom .. I’ll be sharing that project soon ! Hope you are having a wonderful week so far 

I used a shot of espresso 
Ice 🧊 
1/4 cup of caramel creamer 
1/4 cup of condensed milk 
Mexican cajeta (caramel )
Crushed @mazapandelarosa 
Splash of vanilla extract 

#coffeelover #nespresso #coffeetime #coffeecreamer #easyrecipes #reelsinstagram #reelsviral #reelsinsta #zgalleriemoment #homedesign #kitchenisland #kitcheninspo #mexicanartist #mexicana #victorville #selflove
